T02TD1425E:171a-1: shr'i tsa kra samb'a ra n'a ma sha ta aashta k'am sto tra /
T02TD1425E:171a-3: dpal 'khor lo sdom pa'i mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa'i bstod pa /
T02TD1425E:171a-4: dpal rdo rje mkha' 'gro la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1425E:171b-0: bskal pa'i me @171b ltar 'bar ba'i 'jigs pa'i skur ldan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-1: khros pas 'jigs mdzad mtsho skyes sngon po'i sku mdog bzhin //
T02TD1425E:171b-2: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor steng bzhugs kha tv'am ga dang ni //
T02TD1425E:171b-3: rdo rje bsnams shing aom aom yi ge dag pa yis //
T02TD1425E:171b-4: tshangs pa dang ni khyab 'jug drag po'i lha dag gi //
T02TD1425E:171b-5: mgo rnams bcad mdzad nas ni dbu la rnam brgyan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-6: h'um h'um phat phat ta ta yi ge 'khor ldan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-7: mi yi sengge zil mnan nas ni 'jigs mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-8: thugs rje chen pos sbrul pa'i 'khor lo'i tshul bskyed pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-9: dza: h'um bam ho: dpal mo'i nu ma rab tu mnan //
T02TD1425E:171b-10: bde bar gshegs pas dbu gtsug la ni rnam brgyan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-11: lha rnams kun gyi dbu gtsug zhabs kyis mnan mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-12: aa la la yi sgras ni bgegs rnams skrag mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-13: cang te'u 'khrol zhing khyab 'jug drag po'i pags pa bsnams //
T02TD1425E:171b-14: rdo rje lha mo rnams kyi 'khor los sgyur mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-15: hu lu hu lu dzi dzi tram tram dzam dzam sgrogs //
T02TD1425E:171b-16: rgyu mas brgyus pa'i mgo bo'i phreng ba'i rgyan ldan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-17: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i gzugs kyis 'jigs byed glu len pa /
T02TD1425E:171b-18: krum krum dang ni hu lu hu lus myos mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-19: rdo rje mkha' 'gro rnam par brgyan pa yi //
T02TD1425E:171b-20: dur khrod du ni gar dang ha la ha la'i sgras //
T02TD1425E:171b-21: gnod sbyin rnams ni rab tu skrag par mdzad pa des //
T02TD1425E:171b-22: rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma yi glus ni rab bskul ba //
T02TD1425E:171b-23: sha dang khrag dang rgyu ma nang khrol gsol bar mdzad //
T02TD1425E:171b-24: ham ham aa aa'i sgras ni lha rnams gsal mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-25: thod pa klad pas bkang nas gsol phyir phyag na bsnams //
T02TD1425E:171b-26: ka ha kha ha'i bzhad sgras 'khor ba 'jigs mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-27: mi bzad dur khrod rnams kyi rus pa'i rgyan ldan pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-28: rdo rje ha har bzhad pas khams gsum rgyal mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-29: ha ha hi hi dza dza'i yi ges sdigs mdzub mdzad //
T02TD1425E:171b-30: ha ha bzhad pas ri bo rtse nas bsgyel mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-31: rnal 'byor ma dang dpa' rnams hri hri sgrogs pas 'bod //
T02TD1425E:171b-32: mi yi seng ge rtse gsum gyis 'gugs sems can don mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:171b-33: mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal bzhi sku mdog sngon por ldan //
T02TD1425E:171b-34: brum brum sgrogs shing phyag rgya chen por bskyed mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:172a-1: stong 'gyu ba'i ljags ni phyung nas kyang //
T02TD1425E:172a-2: rdo rje dril bu mda' dang gzhu la kram kram sgrogs //
T02TD1425E:172a-3: g-yon brkyang ba dang sbrul rnams kyis ni dbu brgyan cing //
T02TD1425E:172a-4: bskal pa grangs med sems can don mdzad mi 'dor ba //
T02TD1425E:172a-5: ha na da ha phat phat sgrogs shing skyob mdzad pa ;
T02TD1425E:172a-6: / rnal 'byor stobs kyis rgyal ba'i mdzad pa rnams mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:172a-7: dngos dang dngos med min zhing bsgom dang rdo rje can //
T02TD1425E:172a-8: tsa ta tsa ta gram gram kham kham sgrogs mdzad pa //
T02TD1425E:172a-9: sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs kyi spros pa stong pa nyid //
T02TD1425E:172a-10: rol pa'i lta bas dri ma ma lus bral ba dang //
T02TD1425E:172a-11: go lu go lu dzam dzam yam yam sgrogs pas zhi ba dang //
T02TD1425E:172a-12: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i ting 'dzin bzhugs pa'i mthu mnga' ba //
T02TD1425E:172a-13: mam mam sgras ni bde ba chen po'i bdag nyid can //
T02TD1425E:172a-14: thugs rje chen pos rjes 'brel sems can mi gtong ba'i //
T02TD1425E:172a-15: brtan g-yo'i rang bzhin he ru ka dpal phyag 'tshal bstod ;
T02TD1425E:172a-16: / mkha' 'gro'i dam tshig a'a li k'a li'i sbyor ba ste //
T02TD1425E:172a-17: rigs lnga'i bde gshegs bcom ldan 'das kyis bshad du gsol //
T02TD1425E:172a-18: lha dang drang srong rnams ni phyag 'tshal brjod pa yis //
T02TD1425E:172a-19: he ru ka dpal gsang ba'i sku 'dzin der nges 'gyur //
T02TD1425E:172a-20: dpal ldan 'khor lo sdom pa'i mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa'i bstod pa rdzogs so//
